  "title": "Client Service Consultant (Luxury Goods) Office based",
  "description": "<p><strong>Our client is a reputable international luxury goods MNC that has retail stores all over the world.</strong></p><p><strong>Working Schedule: 5 day work week including weekends</strong><br /><strong>Work Timing: Shift hours, no overnight shifts</strong><br /><strong>Working Location: East working location (Office based) - Tampines</strong></p><p><br /></p><ul><li>Facilitate online and phone sales in order to reach set goals and objectives</li><li>Handle Inbound and outbound customer contact via telephone, e-mail, live chat and other (social) media from customers within the SEAO region</li><li>Assist in coordination and communication between Clients and various channels (Stores, Repair Centre, Client Services Overseas, RMS, Stocks etc)</li><li>Coordinating events nationally and internationally, RSVP of VIP Clients and Media (Events, Openings, Exhibitions)</li><li>Outbound calls to Clients includes invites to events and Client Satisfaction Surveys</li></ul><p><br /></p><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Min. 2 years experience in call centre environment.</li><li><strong>Strong communication skills in spoken and written English.</strong></li><li>Possess a good learning attitude and is customer service oriented.</li><li>Has working knowledge in Microsoft Office</li><li>Willing to work on weekends and public holidays as per schedule.</li></ul><p><br /></p><p><strong>Interested candidates may send their updated resume to gareth@quantumcareer.com</strong></p>",
